        "mainbody": "'''Burlan Almaether''' was the acting High Priest of the [[Temple of Gond Wondermaker]] in [[Tilverton]] in the 1350s–1360s [[DR]].",
        "Activities": "Burlan was the leader of Gond's faithful in Tilverton after the disappearance of [[Gharri]] in [[1357 DR]] – the temple's previous High Priest. His congregation within the temple consisted of 26 other priests and 39 followers, and he took the role of acting High Priest until [[Gond]] delivered a divine sign to officially assign the replacement."
